{"word":"G4687 - σπείρω - speírō - spi'-ro - Sow","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σπείρω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>speírō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>spi'-ro"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Sow"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விதை, விதைக்கப்படு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to sow, scatter seed"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Probably strengthened from <a href=\"#/G4685 - σπάω - spáō - spah'-o/4685\">G4685</a> (through the idea of <i>extending</i>); to <i>scatter</i>, that is, <i>sow</i> (literally or figuratively): - sow (-er), receive seed."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4586 - σεμνός - semnós - sem-nos'/4586\">G4586</a>, <a href=\"#/G4687 - σπείρω - speírō - spi'-ro/4687\">G4687</a>, <a href=\"#/G4690 - σπέρμα - spérma - sper'-mah/4690\">G4690</a>, <a href=\"#/G4691 - σπερμολόγος - spermológos - sper-mol-og'-os/4691\">G4691</a>, <a href=\"#/G4701 - σπορά - sporá - spor-ah'/4701\">G4701</a>, <a href=\"#/G4702 - σπόριμος - spórimos - spor'-ee-mos/4702\">G4702</a>, <a href=\"#/G4703 - σπόρος - spóros - spro'-os/4703\">G4703</a>"}]}